                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7374" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1153</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7715 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">乳业常胜将军——伊利的三把营销之斧</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Ever-victorious Dairy Industry——Yili’s three marketing axes</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">雷芳，王琢</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东华理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古伊利实业集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">伊利；战略定位；营销策略；乳制品</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Yili; Strategic Positioning;Marketing Strategy;Dairy Products</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">伊利作为全国行业规模最大、生产产品线最全的乳制品公司，业绩多年稳居亚洲第一，从最初来自呼伦贝尔草原的一家合作养牛协作小组，到目前在全球乳业排行榜位列第五，短短三十年的时间实现了实力的快速增长和品牌价值的极度飞跃。其一路走强的背后是伊利对精准营销的个性化理解。本案例以伊利为研究对象，聚焦其品牌成长问题。重点介绍了伊利市场营销发展的三把关键之斧，具体分析其如何把握前瞻性、创新性和敏锐性来支撑其定位，打造出“伊利即品质”的品牌形象。本案例旨在引导学生加深对产品定位和精准营销的理解，提高学生用以分析和解决现实问题的能力，启发他们针对企业在品牌管理方面的相关问题和在未来可能面临的挑战进行深入的思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As the largest dairy company with the most completed product lines in our country, Yili has been ranked No. 1 in Asia for many years. From a cattle raising cooperative group originally from the Hulunbuir grassland to the fifth in the global dairy industry rankings, it has achieved rapid growth in strength and extreme leap in brand value in just 30 years.The reasons for yili’s success are precision marketing, lean operation and accurate management of the correct control. This case takes Yili as the research object and focuses on its brand growth. It focuses on the introduction of the three key axes of Yili&#39;s marketing development, and specifically analyzes how to grasp the forward-looking, innovative and acuity to support its positioning, so as to create the brand image of &quot;Yili is quality&quot;. This case guides students to deepen their understanding of product positioning and precision marketing. Improve students&#39; ability to analyze and solve practical problems, and inspire them to think deeply about the relevant problems of enterprise brand management and the possible challenges in the future.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《品牌营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">市场营销环境分析；整合营销理论；目标市场理论；产品定位差异化；社会化媒体营销理论；SWOT分析</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-07</td>
                            </tr>
